{"slug":"bosch-service-center-mumbai","title":"Bosch Service Center Mumbai","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\">\r\n\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>Bosch Service Center Mumbai \u2013 Doorstep Appliance Repair<\/title>\r\n    <meta name=\"description\"\r\n        content=\"Expert doorstep repair for Bosch washing machines, refrigerators, ACs and microwaves in Mumbai. Independent specialist technicians.\">\r\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https:\/\/fonts.googleapis.com\">\r\n    <link href=\"https:\/\/fonts.googleapis.com\/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\r\n    <style>\r\n        :root {\r\n            --p: #E20015;\r\n            --bg: #f8fafc;\r\n            --white: #fff;\r\n            --dark: #1e293b;\r\n            --gray: #475569;\r\n            --border: #e2e8f0;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        * {\r\n            margin: 0;\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n            box-sizing: border-box;\r\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        body {\r\n            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;\r\n            background: var(--bg);\r\n            color: var(--dark);\r\n            overflow-x: hidden;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        header {\r\n            position: fixed;\r\n            top: 0;\r\n            left: 0;\r\n            right: 0;\r\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);\r\n            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);\r\n            padding: 1rem 5%;\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            justify-content: space-between;\r\n            align-items: center;\r\n            z-index: 999;\r\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--p);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .logo {\r\n            font-weight: 900;\r\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\r\n            color: var(--p);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        nav a {\r\n            text-decoration: none;\r\n            color: var(--gray);\r\n            font-weight: 700;\r\n            font-size: 0.78rem;\r\n            text-transform: uppercase;\r\n            margin-left: 1.5rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .hero {\r\n            padding: 10rem 5% 4rem;\r\n            max-width: 900px;\r\n            margin: 0 auto;\r\n            text-align: center;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .hero .pill {\r\n            display: inline-block;\r\n            background: #fdf2f2;\r\n            color: var(--p);\r\n            border: 1px solid #fecaca;\r\n            padding: 5px 14px;\r\n            font-size: 0.7rem;\r\n            font-weight: 900;\r\n            text-transform: uppercase;\r\n            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .hero h1 {\r\n            font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 4rem);\r\n            font-weight: 900;\r\n            line-height: 1.1;\r\n            letter-spacing: -1px;\r\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .hero h1 span {\r\n            color: var(--p);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .hero p {\r\n            font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 3vw, 1.2rem);\r\n            color: var(--gray);\r\n            max-width: 700px;\r\n            margin: 0 auto;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .wrap {\r\n            padding: 3rem 5%;\r\n            max-width: 1300px;\r\n            margin: 0 auto;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .box {\r\n            background: var(--white);\r\n            border: 1px solid var(--border);\r\n            padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .sec-title {\r\n            font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);\r\n            font-weight: 900;\r\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\r\n            padding-bottom: 0.7rem;\r\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--p);\r\n            display: inline-block;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .grid {\r\n            display: grid;\r\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(270px, 1fr));\r\n            gap: 2rem;\r\n            margin-top: 1.5rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .card {\r\n            background: var(--white);\r\n            border: 1px solid var(--border);\r\n            overflow: hidden;\r\n            transition: 0.3s;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .card:hover {\r\n            transform: translateY(-4px);\r\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .card img {\r\n            width: 100%;\r\n            height: 180px;\r\n            object-fit: cover;\r\n            display: block;\r\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .card-body {\r\n            padding: 1.5rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .card-body h3 {\r\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\r\n            font-weight: 900;\r\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .card-body p {\r\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\r\n            color: var(--gray);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .issues {\r\n            display: grid;\r\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));\r\n            gap: 2rem;\r\n            margin-top: 1.5rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .issue-col h4 {\r\n            font-size: 1rem;\r\n            font-weight: 900;\r\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\r\n            color: var(--p);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .issue-col ul {\r\n            list-style: none;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .issue-col ul li {\r\n            padding: 0.4rem 0 0.4rem 1.5rem;\r\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\r\n            color: var(--gray);\r\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;\r\n            position: relative;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .issue-col ul li::before {\r\n            content: '\u2192';\r\n            position: absolute;\r\n            left: 0;\r\n            color: var(--p);\r\n            font-weight: 700;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .tips {\r\n            background: var(--white);\r\n            border: 1px solid var(--border);\r\n            border-right: 8px solid var(--p);\r\n            padding: 2rem;\r\n            margin-top: 2rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .tips h4 {\r\n            font-weight: 900;\r\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .tips ul {\r\n            list-style: none;\r\n            display: grid;\r\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));\r\n            gap: 0.8rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .tips ul li {\r\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\r\n            color: var(--gray);\r\n            padding-left: 1.5rem;\r\n            position: relative;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .tips ul li::before {\r\n            content: '\u2713';\r\n            position: absolute;\r\n            left: 0;\r\n            color: var(--p);\r\n            font-weight: 900;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        footer {\r\n            background: var(--white);\r\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--p);\r\n            padding: 4rem 5% 2rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .footer-grid {\r\n            display: grid;\r\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));\r\n            gap: 3rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .footer-logo {\r\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\r\n            font-weight: 900;\r\n            color: var(--p);\r\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .note {\r\n            font-size: 0.8rem;\r\n            color: var(--gray);\r\n            font-style: italic;\r\n            margin-top: 1rem;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .footer-bottom {\r\n            text-align: center;\r\n            margin-top: 3rem;\r\n            padding-top: 1.5rem;\r\n            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\r\n            font-size: 0.85rem;\r\n            color: #94a3b8;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .fade {\r\n            opacity: 0;\r\n            transform: translateY(25px);\r\n            transition: 0.7s ease;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .show {\r\n            opacity: 1;\r\n            transform: translateY(0);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        @media(max-width:768px) {\r\n            header {\r\n                flex-direction: column;\r\n                gap: 0.4rem;\r\n                padding: 0.8rem 5%;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            nav a {\r\n                margin-left: 0.8rem;\r\n                font-size: 0.7rem;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .hero {\r\n                padding: 9rem 5% 3rem;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .wrap {\r\n                padding: 2rem 5%;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    <\/style>\r\n<\/head>\r\n\r\n<body>\r\n    <header>\r\n        <div class=\"logo\">BOSCH SERVICE CENTER<\/div>\r\n        <nav>\r\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services<\/a>\r\n            <a href=\"#issues\">Common Issues<\/a>\r\n            <a href=\"#process\">Our Process<\/a>\r\n        <\/nav>\r\n    <\/header>\r\n\r\n    <section class=\"hero\">\r\n        <div class=\"fade\">\r\n            <div class=\"pill\">German Precision \u00b7 Mumbai<\/div>\r\n            <h1>Engineered Care. <span>Restored for You.<\/span><\/h1>\r\n            <p>Expert doorstep servicing for all Bosch appliances across Mumbai \u2014 Serie 6\/8 washing machines, VitaFresh\r\n                fridges, ACs and microwaves. We diagnose, explain, and repair only with your approval.<\/p>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/section>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"wrap fade\" id=\"services\">\r\n        <h2 class=\"sec-title\">Our Services<\/h2>\r\n        <div class=\"grid\">\r\n            <div class=\"card\">\r\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/24x7homeappliances.help\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Screenshot-2025-09-27-223626.png\"\r\n                    alt=\"Bosch Washing Machine Repair\">\r\n                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                    <h3>Washing Machine Repair<\/h3>\r\n                    <p>Serie 6\/8 Front Load and Top Load servicing. EcoSilence drum failures, door seals, drain pump,\r\n                        PCB faults.<\/p>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"card\">\r\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/24x7homeappliances.help\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Screenshot-2025-09-27-223826.png\"\r\n                    alt=\"Bosch Refrigerator Repair\">\r\n                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                    <h3>Refrigerator Repair<\/h3>\r\n                    <p>VitaFresh and NoFrost fridge servicing. Cooling loss, gas recharge, defrost errors, and sensor\r\n                        faults.<\/p>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"card\">\r\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/24x7homeappliances.help\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Screenshot-2025-09-27-223923.png\"\r\n                    alt=\"Bosch Microwave Dishwasher Repair\">\r\n                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                    <h3>Microwave &amp; Dishwasher<\/h3>\r\n                    <p>Solo\/Convection oven repairs and dishwasher drainage, spray arm, and pump motor issues.<\/p>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"wrap fade\" id=\"issues\">\r\n        <div class=\"box\">\r\n            <h2 class=\"sec-title\">Common Issues We Fix<\/h2>\r\n            <div class=\"issues\">\r\n                <div class=\"issue-col\">\r\n                    <h4>Washing Machine<\/h4>\r\n                    <ul>\r\n                        <li>Not draining or spinning<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Drum vibration and noise<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Door lock failure<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Error codes (E17, E18, F21)<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Water leakage<\/li>\r\n                    <\/ul>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"issue-col\">\r\n                    <h4>Refrigerator<\/h4>\r\n                    <ul>\r\n                        <li>Not cooling adequately<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Excessive frost buildup<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Compressor noise<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Water pooling inside<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Display panel errors<\/li>\r\n                    <\/ul>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"issue-col\">\r\n                    <h4>Air Conditioner<\/h4>\r\n                    <ul>\r\n                        <li>Insufficient cooling<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Water dripping indoors<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Remote\/sensor not working<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Compressor tripping<\/li>\r\n                        <li>Unusual noises<\/li>\r\n                    <\/ul>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"tips\">\r\n                <h4>\ud83d\udca1 Laundry Care Tips<\/h4>\r\n                <ul>\r\n                    <li>Empty pockets before washing<\/li>\r\n                    <li>Zip garments; unhook bras<\/li>\r\n                    <li>Separate darks from whites<\/li>\r\n                    <li>Avoid overloading the drum<\/li>\r\n                <\/ul>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"wrap fade\" id=\"process\">\r\n        <div class=\"box\">\r\n            <h2 class=\"sec-title\">Our Repair Process<\/h2>\r\n            <p>We provide doorstep repair and servicing for all major home appliances. Whether you need a washing\r\n                machine, refrigerator, microwave oven, air conditioner or dishwasher fixed, our team aims to reach you\r\n                quickly across Mumbai. Support is available round the clock for booking and queries.<\/p>\r\n            <br>\r\n            <p>Our technicians diagnose the fault in front of you, explain the work required, and proceed only after you\r\n                approve the estimate. We use quality spare parts and offer warranty terms as communicated at the time of\r\n                service.<\/p>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\r\n    <footer>\r\n        <div class=\"footer-grid\">\r\n            <div>\r\n                <div class=\"footer-logo\">BOSCH SERVICE CENTER<\/div>\r\n                <p>Expert restoration team in Mumbai delivering durable and punctual care for all Bosch products.<\/p>\r\n                <p class=\"note\">Independent specialist center \u2014 not brand-authorised unless specified.<\/p>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n            <div>\r\n                <h4 style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;\">Appliances We Service<\/h4>\r\n                <p>Washing Machine<\/p>\r\n                <p>Refrigerator<\/p>\r\n                <p>Air Conditioner<\/p>\r\n                <p>Microwave Oven<\/p>\r\n                <p>Dishwasher<\/p>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n            <div>\r\n                <h4 style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;\">Service Areas<\/h4>\r\n                <p>Andheri \u00b7 Bandra \u00b7 Dadar<\/p>\r\n                <p>Thane \u00b7 Navi Mumbai \u00b7 Kurla<\/p>\r\n                <p>Borivali \u00b7 Malad \u00b7 Mulund<\/p>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n        <div class=\"footer-bottom\">\u00a9 2025 Expert Technician Mumbai. All rights reserved.<\/div>\r\n    <\/footer>\r\n    <script>\r\n        const obs = new IntersectionObserver(e => e.forEach(x => { if (x.isIntersecting) x.target.classList.add('show') }), { threshold: 0.08 });\r\n        document.querySelectorAll('.fade').forEach(el => obs.observe(el));\r\n    <\/script>\r\n<\/body>\r\n\r\n<\/html>","css":"","is_home":false,"allow_in_menu":false,"status":"published","updated":"2026-03-28 16:16:44","meta_description":"Bosch service center Mumbai \u2014 washing machine, fridge, AC, microwave & TV. Different coverage & specialist focus. Independent provider.","og_image":"","page_template":"canvas"}